PanelIyagi is a proprietary panel and taskbar software
designed specifically for Ubuntu Linux systems using the GNOME desktop environment.
The software is distributed only as executable files; the source code is not publicly available.

1. Free Usage
PanelIyagi may be used freely for any purpose, including personal, commercial, educational, governmental, and organizational use.

2. GNOME Shell Extension
GNOME Shell extension included in PanelIyagi is licensed under **GPL-2.0-or-later**.
Follow the license terms when modifying or redistributing the extension.

3. Distribution and Usage
Anyone may freely install, package, and redistribute PanelIyagi.
It can be used in any manner, including Linux distribution repositories, software centers, Snap/Flatpak, AppImage, GitHub, internal enterprise systems, ISO images, or physical media.

4. Trademarks
The name "PanelIyagi" may be used to identify the original software.

